OL,3,CMurderer Victor Farrant dies in prison
OL,4,Cweeks after release bid on health
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FVictor Farrant, a rapist who was
OL,8,Fserving a whole-life sentence after
OL,9,Fmurdering his former girlfriend, has
OL,10,Fdied in prison.
OL,12,FThe Prison Service said Farrant, 74,
OL,13,Fdied at HMP Wakefield on Friday.
OL,15,FThe children of Glenda Hoskins, whom
OL,16,Fhe murdered, said his death ends an
OL,17,F"agonising two months" since they
OL,18,Fheard and everyone should "feel safer
OL,19,Fthat this repeat-offender psychopath
OL,20,Fwill not strike again".
