OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FHe had been suffering from a
OL,8,Flongstanding health condition and a
OL,9,Fcoroner will now look in to the cause
OL,10,Fof his death.
OL,12,FFarrant was convicted of the murder of
OL,13,FMs Hoskins, 44, his former girlfriend
OL,14,Fand mother-of-three, in Portsmouth,
OL,15,Fand the attempted murder of Ann
OL,16,FFidler, 45, in Eastleigh in 1996.
