OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FSentencing him to jail for life Mr
OL,8,FJustice Butterfield, sitting at
OL,9,FWinchester Crown Court in 1998, said
OL,10,FFarrant was so dangerous that he
OL,11,Fshould "never be released".
OL,13,FITV Meridian's Richard Slee spoke to
OL,14,FGlenda Hoskins' son Iain in March,
OL,15,Fover his concerns about Farrant's wish
OL,16,Ffor early release.
