OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FIn a joint statement on Monday Ms
OL,8,FHoskins children, Iain, Katie and
OL,9,FDavid, said: "Farrant's whole life
OL,10,Fsentence and the judges remarks that
OL,11,Fhe should die in prison should have
OL,12,Fbeen respected.
OL,14,F"However, Farrant's death, like his
OL,15,Fimprisonment, changes nothing for us,
OL,16,Fthe circumstances and death of our
OL,17,Fmother, Glenda Hoskins, will haunt us
OL,18,Ffor the rest of our lives.
