OL,3,CMurderer Victor Farrant dies in prison
OL,4,Cweeks after release bid on health
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FEarlier this year Ms Hoskins family
OL,8,Fsaid they had been contacted by
OL,9,Fofficials who said that Farrant was
OL,10,Fbeing considered for compassionate
OL,11,Fleave as he had been diagnosed with
OL,12,Fterminal cancer and could have months
OL,13,Fto live.
OL,15,FA Multi-Agency Public Protection
OL,16,FArrangements (Mappa) meeting in April
OL,17,Flooked at the case which the family
OL,18,Fsaid had been passed on to the prison
OL,19,Fgovernor to decide whether to make a
OL,20,Fformal application for his release.
