OL,3,CMurderer Victor Farrant dies in prison
OL,4,Cweeks after release bid on health
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FFarrant was jailed in November 1988
OL,8,Ffor 12 years for rape and other
OL,9,Foffences, but just weeks after he was
OL,10,Freleased on November 7 1995, he beat
OL,11,FMs Fidler at her home in Eastleigh,
OL,12,FHampshire.
OL,14,FSix weeks later, he murdered
OL,15,Faccountant Mrs Hoskins at her luxury
OL,16,Fwaterside home in Portsmouth by
OL,17,Fpushing her under the water in the
OL,18,Fbath.
