OL,3,CMurderer Victor Farrant dies in prison
OL,4,Cweeks after release bid on health
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,FHe left her body in the attic where it
OL,8,Fwas found by her 15-year-old daughter
OL,9,FKatie.
OL,11,FAfter killing Ms Hoskins, Farrant went
OL,12,Fon the run and was eventually found in
OL,13,Fthe south of France.
OL,15,FAfter hearing about his death, the
OL,16,FHoskins family said: "This brings to a
OL,17,Fclose an agonising two months since we
OL,18,Fwere contacted by the Justice
OL,19,Fdepartment about plans being made for
OL,20,Fhis early release.
