OL,3,CMurderer Victor Farrant dies in prison
OL,4,Cweeks after release bid on health
OL,5,Cgrounds
OL,7,F"As victims the lack of information
OL,8,Fand clarity of the steps in this
OL,9,Fprocess was bewildering and
OL,10,Funnecessary.
OL,12,F"Our feeling is, while still
OL,13,Frespecting the judicial process a huge
OL,14,Famount of pain and mental anguish
OL,15,Fcould have been spared by allowing us
OL,16,Fbetter access to the factual elements
OL,17,Fof his petition for release."
OL,19,FA Prison Service spokesman said:
OL,20,F"Victor Farrant died on May 3 at HMP
OL,21,FWakefield.
